596
00:28:04,880 --> 00:28:06,980
Childhood friendships are precious,

597
00:28:07,410 --> 00:28:10,390
but after growing up, you still have to rely on yourself.

598
00:28:10,660 --> 00:28:12,610
Then I'll just refuse to grow up.

599
00:28:16,880 --> 00:28:20,570
Friends walk together for life.

600
00:28:20,590 --> 00:28:24,540
Those days won't come again.

601
00:28:24,560 --> 00:28:28,610
One promise for a lifetime.

602
00:28:28,640 --> 00:28:30,590
One lifetime of friendship.

603
