610
00:28:45,430 --> 00:28:46,440
Fenghua,

611
00:28:46,770 --> 00:28:48,740
after they arrived,

612
00:28:48,990 --> 00:28:50,710
things have been smooth for us.

613
00:28:50,880 --> 00:28:52,660
We're going to take over

614
00:28:52,700 --> 00:28:54,280
Haidian District soon.

615
00:28:55,470 --> 00:28:57,650
If you want to join now, it's not too late.

616
00:28:58,750 --> 00:29:00,950
