617
00:29:02,060 --> 00:29:04,260
Celebrating our success is priority.

618
00:29:04,960 --> 00:29:06,720
Poaching you is second.

619
00:29:08,060 --> 00:29:09,130
I know

620
00:29:09,360 --> 00:29:11,540
