621
00:29:11,570 --> 00:29:13,540
Fenghua, if you're willing to come,

622
00:29:13,570 --> 00:29:15,450
I'll take all your employees.

623
00:29:16,480 --> 00:29:17,490
To do what?

624
00:29:17,700 --> 00:29:19,030
To do food delivery.

625
00:29:19,060 --> 00:29:20,140
What else?

626
00:29:21,530 --> 00:29:23,800
I trust the people you've trained.

627
00:29:24,330 --> 00:29:25,460
I'm telling you,

628
00:29:26,510 --> 00:29:28,380
the income from food delivery

629
00:29:28,390 --> 00:29:31,110
will definitely be much higher than express delivery.

630
00:29:31,350 --> 00:29:32,120
It's a win-win.

631
00:29:34,800 --> 00:29:36,310
What if I refuse?

632
00:29:36,340 --> 00:29:37,760
Why would you refuse?

633
00:29:37,800 --> 00:29:39,310
I'm not interested. Is that okay?

634
00:29:39,340 --> 00:29:41,190
Why aren't you interested?

635
00:29:46,470 --> 00:29:47,880
Alright, alright.

636
00:29:48,220 --> 00:29:50,490
I'm sorry. I was wrong.

637
00:29:51,740 --> 00:29:54,650
If you really don't want to come, I can't force you.

638
00:29:54,710 --> 00:29:57,000
But you should at least tell me your actual situation.

639
00:29:57,030 --> 00:29:57,920
Why?

640
00:29:59,770 --> 00:30:02,100
I came here today for entertainment,

641
00:30:02,160 --> 00:30:03,850
