759
00:36:16,150 --> 00:36:17,680
With the information he's researched,

760
00:36:17,700 --> 00:36:19,460
he could change careers and open a matchmaking agency.

761
00:36:20,600 --> 00:36:21,360
Yes.

762
00:36:22,280 --> 00:36:23,140
Fenghua,

763
00:36:23,890 --> 00:36:25,360
you need to

764
00:36:25,390 --> 00:36:27,790
keep an eye on Wanghe for me.

765
00:36:27,810 --> 00:36:29,500
Don't let him mess around.

766
00:36:30,270 --> 00:36:32,940
Don't worry, he's doing quite well.

767
00:36:32,980 --> 00:36:35,300
Xingchi and Haikuo are both working for him now.

768
00:36:35,450 --> 00:36:36,810
He even tried to poach me.

769
00:36:36,830 --> 00:36:37,970
I firmly refused.

770
00:36:39,100 --> 00:36:40,050
Why?

771
00:36:41,070 --> 00:36:42,880
If you have any concerns, tell me.

772
00:36:42,900 --> 00:36:44,220
I'll go scold him later.

773
00:36:44,820 --> 00:36:45,830
I'm not concerned.

774
00:36:46,780 --> 00:36:48,030
I'm doing fine on my own.

775
00:36:48,060 --> 00:36:49,650
