776
00:36:49,800 --> 00:36:51,440
I can't be bothered to listen to his nonsense.

777
00:36:57,080 --> 00:36:58,480
You little girl.

778
00:36:58,660 --> 00:37:02,800
[Monopoly]

779
00:37:08,020 --> 00:37:11,310
I'll build another house

780
00:37:12,030 --> 00:37:13,130
and put it here.

781
00:37:14,150 --> 00:37:16,640
I've connected all these, haven't I?

782
00:37:17,410 --> 00:37:19,920
You just said you guys also poached Fenghua.

783
00:37:20,020 --> 00:37:21,100
Yes, that's right.

784
00:37:21,120 --> 00:37:23,130
Wanghe has always wanted Fenghua to come.

785
00:37:23,190 --> 00:37:24,100
Fenghua refuses.

786
00:37:25,000 --> 00:37:26,670
Why? Is it because the pay is too low?

787
00:37:26,910 --> 00:37:28,240
It's not about the money.

788
00:37:28,260 --> 00:37:29,550
