801
00:38:01,650 --> 00:38:03,990
Wouldn't that completely ruin any chances for them?

802
00:38:05,950 --> 00:38:07,310
Does Wanghe know about this?

803
00:38:09,190 --> 00:38:11,620
He should be aware of it in his heart.

804
00:38:12,620 --> 00:38:13,990
No one dares to say anything.

805
00:38:14,830 --> 00:38:15,790
Why?

806
00:38:16,470 --> 00:38:18,170
If this kind of thing is said out loud,

807
00:38:18,230 --> 00:38:19,820
it's fine if it works out.

808
00:38:19,980 --> 00:38:20,800
If it doesn't,

809
00:38:22,350 --> 00:38:23,330
after that,

810
00:38:23,360 --> 00:38:24,800
they can't even be friends anymore.

811
00:38:44,150 --> 00:38:45,300
You're awake.

812
00:38:48,830 --> 00:38:50,180
When did you arrive?

813
00:38:50,440 --> 00:38:51,230
Last night.

814
00:38:51,470 --> 00:38:52,430
He drank,

815
00:38:52,460 --> 00:38:53,780
so I drove here.

816
00:38:55,420 --> 00:38:56,270
Have a seat.

817
00:39:00,470 --> 00:39:01,030
Dad.

818
00:39:01,170 --> 00:39:02,050
I'm fine, I'm fine.

819
00:39:02,070 --> 00:39:02,830
I'm really okay.

820
00:39:02,950 --> 00:39:04,800
Just a small cut on my stomach.

821
00:39:04,820 --> 00:39:05,550
It'll heal in a couple of days.

822
00:39:07,460 --> 00:39:08,770
What if it wasn't your stomach?

823
00:39:08,900 --> 00:39:09,990
