828
00:39:14,880 --> 00:39:16,230
That's enough.

829
00:39:16,270 --> 00:39:17,380
You're nagging more than my mom.

830
00:39:17,400 --> 00:39:18,630
Is it a crime to be a Good Samaritan?

831
00:39:18,670 --> 00:39:19,700
