835
00:39:24,010 --> 00:39:25,680
Your dad can only have liquid food now.

836
00:39:25,710 --> 00:39:26,900
Are you going to eat in front of him?

837
00:39:26,940 --> 00:39:27,940
That's inhumane.

838
00:39:28,370 --> 00:39:29,010
Let's go.

839
00:39:29,470 --> 00:39:31,240
Don't move. I'll be back soon.

840
00:39:33,160 --> 00:39:34,440
You talk too much.

841
00:39:46,450 --> 00:39:47,540
I've noticed.

842
00:39:48,060 --> 00:39:49,180
